statements.sql: select count(*) as aggregate from `categories` inner join `news_categories` on `categories`.`id` = `news_categories`.`category_id` inner join `news` on `news_categories`.`news_id` = `news`.`id` left join `reporters` on `reporters`.`id` = `news`.`reporter_id` left join `guests` on `guests`.`id` = `news`.`guest_id` where `categories`.`slug` = 'bollywood'

select `news`.`sub_title`, `news`.`slug` as `news_slug`, `news`.`title`, `news`.`short_description`, `news`.`description`, `news`.`publish_date`, `categories`.`slug` as `category_slug`, `categories`.`name` as `category`, IFNULL(reporters.name,guests.name) as author, IFNULL(news.reporter_id,news.guest_id) as author_type from `categories` inner join `news_categories` on `categories`.`id` = `news_categories`.`category_id` inner join `news` on `news_categories`.`news_id` = `news`.`id` left join `reporters` on `reporters`.`id` = `news`.`reporter_id` left join `guests` on `guests`.`id` = `news`.`guest_id` where `categories`.`slug` = 'bollywood' limit 10 offset 0

select `categories`.`name`, `categories`.`slug` from `categories` inner join `category_positions` on `categories`.`id` = `category_positions`.`category_id` where `parent_id` is null and `is_active` = 1 and `categories`.`deleted_at` is null and `category_positions`.`detail_header_position` is not null order by `category_positions`.`detail_header_position` asc limit 11
